PersonalMission.Name: LT-7: The SPG Hunter
PersonalMission.Description: Artillery is a priority target for light tanks. Destroying enemy SPGs will greatly increase your team's chance of victory.
PersonalMission.Hint: Taking out enemy artillery is not easy. Wait until your teammates have gotten the enemy's attention, and then rush to the enemy SPGs. When you engage them, try not to cross in front of their guns. Instead, hit them from the sides and rear.

Primary.Conditions: •  Spot and cause damage to 2 SPGs
